data.description: CUTE AS A BUG, CLEAN AS A WHISTLE...this home exudes good old fashioned charm that's hard not to like. It's comfortable and really spacious for the price, offering lots of storage room, 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, lower level is unfinished but is all useable space. Color scheme is neutral for the most part. Really all that needs to be done here is MOVE IN.
data.whatILove: EXTREMELY WELL TAKEN CARE OF THROUGHOUT THE YEARS, YOU CAN BUY THIS ONE WITH CONFIDENCE.
